<br>
For the lower levels I highly recommend doing kill tasks! Our speed is our advantage here and you will always be able to solo the mobs assigned. To get a kill task, find the named guards in any town and &quot;/say task&quot; to them. They will ask you to kill a particular mob then return for exp reward. Each town has named guards, so if you can't get a task in one town try another until you find a guard that will give them to you.<br>
<br>
There is a bank to store items. Look for the npc Vaultkeeper in Jord inside the big building up the top of the stairs. Gna Faste also has a vaultkeeper in the hut.<br>
<br>
For weapons, I would highly recommend purchasing a player-crafted weapon for your level and enchanting it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
